{"tid":1752993,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家還返銀髮族 中年人 非香港出世手足一個公道","createTime":"2019-11-25T00:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T07:50:56.000Z","uid":44925,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c1ced1cad64059b8b8e780b1cb5fbf168587f727","tid":1752993,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:52:17.000Z","msg":"其實 有去過遊行 抗爭 投票都知<br />\n抗爭者唔止係身份證Y同Z手足 <br />\n冇錯 的確係一大堆廢老廢中 特別係觀塘九龍城特別多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但中年人同老人家唔等於藍絲</span><br />\n我見過一位婆婆聲淚俱下擋係防暴面前為左幫班後生仔走 <br />\n我見過好多呀叔呀伯踢住拖係度屌柒班防暴狗<br />\n被捕人士入面唔止1,2字頭 最老有7字頭被捕者 王婆婆呢家仲係深圳還押緊<br />\n<br />\n仲有 好多後生手足佢地身份證唔係Y字頭 但係出生地冇得選擇 個人意志有得選擇<br />\n佢地一樣為香港付出好多 身份證號碼除左一個英文字母外其實冇意思<br />\n<br />\n呢個運動年青人付出左最多 但請大家都唔好忘記其他人都一直支持緊我地"},{"pid":"fd1874f1c6e2a6f6f825699f4537398e266744d4","tid":1752993,"uid":68598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:57:17.000Z","msg":"應該強調 今次係所以真香港人都參與<br />\n唔指後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各有各用處"},{"pid":"b457aa1d03c492dbae73a06861b05dc79a0a4b20","tid":1752993,"uid":41604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:00:29.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a9aa195bf23e6b21f84a76c9f8979822a474ba","tid":1752993,"uid":101756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bff7355385d6273aa16461418bbc985bd5439a","tid":1752993,"uid":101756,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:02:58.000Z","msg":"見到行唔郁果D銀髮都出黎遊行真係喊左"},{"pid":"cdb34b929e5088c76597360f97d2893168ce7d7a","tid":1752993,"uid":88517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:04:37.000Z","msg":"啱，唔係個個都廢老<br />\n有銀髮手足<br />\n<br />\n守護孩子就係個例子"},{"pid":"02a13ad6f9cbd5bb2879c0ba6d3a5909df6771cc","tid":1752993,"uid":44925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:04:53.000Z","msg":"所以當投票果陣好多手足見到後生仔唔夠多好似好擔心<br />\n其實好多大人佢地可能無膽上前線 但叫佢地排隊投票佢地係義不容辭"},{"pid":"a9ddbe8b017c8e81da84a200b3f643f810063a5d","tid":1752993,"uid":18401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:13:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b39d2d8ae4f0ebc7f1904aaad976484eb33a609e","tid":1752993,"uid":44925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd1874f1c6e2a6f6f825699f4537398e266744d4","tid":1752993,"uid":68598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:57:17.000Z","msg":"應該強調 今次係所以真香港人都參與<br />\n唔指後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各有各用處"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:53:36.000Z","msg":"今次唔止係年青人既運動 係全香港人既運動"},{"pid":"01c80007a342af56528acecf493f54ebff94c270","tid":1752993,"uid":44925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cdb34b929e5088c76597360f97d2893168ce7d7a","tid":1752993,"uid":88517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:04:37.000Z","msg":"啱，唔係個個都廢老<br />\n有銀髮手足<br />\n<br />\n守護孩子就係個例子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:07:58.000Z","msg":"冇錯 唔好亂咁標籤人係藍絲"},{"pid":"6d77c919e2c93d8fac0cdc40363136068f5edb79","tid":1752993,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58dc284e5df3edc2870efb38091bc331396e4bd","tid":1752993,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:50:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}